# First understand what is happening

Your project needs to store tour package data like:

```text id="ew6u1w"
Manali Trip
Goa Trip
Kerala Trip
```

Each package has information:

```text id="f7t1tk"
title
destination
price
duration
available seats
description
```

Where should this data be stored?

Inside MySQL database.

Database stores data in **tables**.

So we need a table like:

| id | title       | destination | price |
| -- | ----------- | ----------- | ----- |
| 1  | Manali Trip | Manali      | 12000 |
| 2  | Goa Trip    | Goa         | 8000  |

