# But Java cannot directly understand MySQL tables

Java understands:

```text id="npv6z0"
classes
objects
```

Database understands:

```text id="2q37zt"
tables
rows
```

So Spring Boot + JPA converts:

```text id="0n9ikd"
Java class  ↔  Database table
```

This is why we create:

```text id="h3x9ww"
TourPackage.java
```

